if you don't understand the words.

277
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:48,640
Buddy,

278
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:50,999
you want me to refer to the dictionary
word by word?

279
00:15:51,744 --> 00:15:52,903
Look at the long paragraphs.

280
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:54,799
