300
00:16:37,119 --> 00:16:37,799
Enough.

301
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:39,119
Get to it already.

302
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,640
There's trouble at your 11 o'clock.

303
00:16:59,640 --> 00:17:01,720
