As a veteran,

534
00:31:01,528 --> 00:31:02,800
I should give up my seat.

535
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:07,480
Don't worry, I'm fine.

536
00:31:14,320 --> 00:31:15,200
Listen.

537
00:31:16,439 --> 00:31:17,480
No matter where you go,

538
00:31:19,275 --> 00:31:21,080
